Banking Application - Using core Java

Two Types Users:(Entities/Models)
i)Bank Employee
ii)Bank Account Holder(User)


Database :(3 tables)
1.Bank_Employee(b_id,b_name,password)
2.Bank_User(accId,accName,address,avail_balance,password)
3.Transaction(tid,accid,amount,transaction-type,date)


Operations:
Bank_Employee -> openAccount(),checkUserAccountDetails(),login(),logout(),changePassword(),removeUser(),UpdateUserDetails(),dipositAmount()
bank_user -> login(),logout(),deposit(),withdraw(),checkProfile(),checkAvailBalance(), updateDetails(),fundTranser()


Employee -> validate the login(userid/password) -> show the menu

1.openAccount
2.checkUserAccountDetails
3.changePassword
4.removeUser
5.UpdateUserDetails
6.dipositAmount
7.Logout


bank User->validate the login(userid/password) ->show the menu

1.deposit Amount
2.withdraw
3.checkProfile
4.checkAvailBalance
5.updateDetails
6.fundTransfer
7.Recent transaction details
7.logout








